sentences: Begum Parveen Sultana (Assamese: বেগম পাৰৱীন চুলতানা; born May 1950) is an Indian Hindustani classical singer of the Patiala Gharana.
She was awarded the Padma Bhushan by the Government of India in 2014 and the Sangeet Natak Akademi Award by the Sangeet Natak Akademi in 1998.
